( { In reply to } 3.Qe2 d4 { is the most logical reaction, because the knight
should retreat back to the 1st rank - } 4.Nd1 e5 5.g3 c5 6.d3 Nc6 7.f4 Bd6 {
and now: } 8.Nf3
